textAnnotations.description:
Barilla
FIORI
n.80
COOKING DIRECTIONS
Get the best from your pasta,
cooking the Italian way
D Bring 4-6 quarts of water to a
boil. Add salt to taste.
2 Add pasta to boiling water.
3 For authentic "al dente" pasta,
boil for 7 minutes, stirring
occasionally. For more tender pasta,
boil an additional minute.
9 Drain well and serve immediately
with your favorite Barilla sauce.
